  <summary date="2024-06-17T16:15:47Z" status="Introduced in House">Paycheck Protection Act

This bill prohibits federal agencies, including the U.S Postal Service, from deducting labor union dues, fees, or political contributions from employee pay. Under current law, an agency must deduct union dues upon receiving a request from an employee.</summary>
